<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ briefing.title }} — 팩트렌즈</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/static/favicon.ico">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <h1 class="site-title">팩트렌즈</h1>
        <p class="tagline">팩트가 검증된 쉬운 뉴스 브리핑</p>
    </header>

    <main class="briefing">
        <h2 class="briefing-title">{{ briefing.title }}</h2>

        {% for article in briefing.articles %}
        <article class="news-card">
            <h3 class="card-headline">{{ article.headline }}</h3>

            <section class="card-summary">
                {% for paragraph in article.summary.split('\n\n') %}
                <p>{{ paragraph }}</p>
                {% endfor %}
            </section>

            <section class="card-verification">
                {% if article.verification_tag == 'verified' %}
                <span class="tag tag--verified">&#x2705; 사실 확인됨</span>
                {% elif article.verification_tag == 'unconfirmed' %}
                <span class="tag tag--unconfirmed">&#x26A0;&#xFE0F; 사실 확인 중</span>
                {% elif article.verification_tag == 'misleading' %}
                <span class="tag tag--misleading">&#x274C; 왜곡/오류</span>
                {% endif %}
                <p class="verification-reason">{{ article.verification_reason }}</p>
                {% if article.verification_tag != 'unconfirmed' and article.evidence_links %}
                <details class="evidence-toggle">
                    <summary>출처 확인하기 ({{ article.evidence_links | length }}건)</summary>
                    <ul class="evidence-list">
                        {% for evidence in article.evidence_links %}
                        <li><a href="{{ evidence.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ evidence.title }}</a></li>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </ul>
                    {% if article.search_entry_point %}
                    <div class="search-widget">
                        {{ article.search_entry_point | safe }}
                    </div>
                    {% endif %}
                </details>
                {% endif %}
            </section>

            <section class="card-sources">
                <h4>원문 보기</h4>
                <ul class="source-list">
                    {% for source in article.source_articles %}
                    <li><a href="{{ source.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ source.publisher }}</a></li>
                    {% endfor %}
                    {% if article.original_url %}
                    <li><a href="{{ article.original_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ article.publisher if article.publisher else '원문' }}</a></li>
                    {% endif %}
                </ul>
            </section>
        </article>
        {% if loop.index == 3 %}
        <div class="mid-support-banner">
            <a class="support-link" href="https://buymeacoffee.com/factlens" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                가짜뉴스 없는 세상, 후원으로 함께 만들어주세요
            </a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <p class="disclaimer">AI 기반 자동 검증이며, 최종 판단은 독자의 몫입니다.</p>
        <a class="support-link" href="https://buymeacoffee.com/factlens" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            가짜뉴스 없는 세상, 후원으로 함께 만들어주세요
        </a>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
